testcase.title: Export Search Service for Company dataset verifying all the column names

steps.title: I am authenticated user accessing "SOAP" API

I pass a "applicationId = ngapi#1756 and userId = API and dataSet = company and searchQuery = cancer and queryLanguage = ssql and returnFields = companyNameDisplay,companyAncestorNameDisplay,companyHqCountry,companyIndicationsKey,companyActionsKey,companyTechnologiesKey,companyDrugDevelopmentActiveCount,companyDrugInactiveCount,companyDealsCount,companyPatentFamilyCountAsOwner,companyPatentFamilyCountAsThirdParty,companyDateAdded,companyWebsite,companyHqInformation,companyCategoryOrganizationType,companyFieldofActivity,companyProfileDisplay,companyBusinessDevInformation and returnLimit = 10 and offset = 0 and expectedValues = expadvsearch_company_079.xls and exportFormat = MS-EXCEL and wrapText = True" as parameter to "asyncExportAdvancedSearchResults" operation
I call poll async "180" times with interval "1" seconds with input "applicationId = ngapi#1756 and userId = API" I should get the response
check the requested file is found in the following path "expadvsearch_company_079.xls"

check for all the columns "Company Name,Parent Company Name,Country/Territory,Key Indications,Key Target-based Actions,Key Technologies,Number of Drugs in Active Development,Number of Inactive Drugs,Number of Deals,Number of Patents as Owner,Number of Patents as Third Party,Added Date,Website,Address,Organization Type,Field of Activity,First Paragraph of Summary,Business Development Contact" in the file
